      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179198/RenderMan_InteractiveDenoiser_Katana.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531541933&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=477\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546179198/RenderMan_InteractiveDenoiser_Katana.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531541933&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"679\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546179219\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_InteractiveDenoiser_Katana.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546179198\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"dd24171f-c59d-42a7-b535-9db2ff76da0b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179198/RenderMan_InteractiveDenoiser_Katana.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531541933&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1800&amp;height=954 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179198/RenderMan_InteractiveDenoiser_Katana.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531541933&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=477 1x\"></span><p /><hr/><h3 id=\"InteractiveDenoiser-ActivateInteractiveDenoising\">Activate Interactive Denoising</h3><p>The interactive denoising option can be found on the PrmanGlobalStatements node</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179198/RenderMan_InteractiveDenoiser_Panel.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531541695&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=145\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546179198/RenderMan_InteractiveDenoiser_Panel.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531541695&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"190\" data-width=\"1178\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546179213\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_InteractiveDenoiser_Panel.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546179198\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"8203dec0-f110-4eff-abb3-9366d41dfd26\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179198/RenderMan_InteractiveDenoiser_Panel.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531541695&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1178&amp;height=190 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179198/RenderMan_InteractiveDenoiser_Panel.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531541695&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=145 1x\"></span><hr/><h3 id=\"InteractiveDenoiser-Preferences\"><strong>Preferences</strong></h3><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179198/RenderMan_InteractiveDenoiser_Prefs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531541695&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=530\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546179198/RenderMan_InteractiveDenoiser_Prefs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531541695&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"754\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546179216\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_InteractiveDenoiser_Prefs.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546179198\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"67a87ee2-8580-4736-af36-d387b0eff69d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179198/RenderMan_InteractiveDenoiser_Prefs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531541695&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1624&amp;height=957 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179198/RenderMan_InteractiveDenoiser_Prefs.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531541695&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=530 1x\"></span><p><strong>Cheap First Pass</strong><br/><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">If checked, the first pass will use a cheaper (slightly faster but lower quality) heuristic.</span></p><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">This can be useful if rendering something that is converging very quickly and you want to prioritize getting a denoised result faster.</span></p><p><strong>Interval</strong><br/><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">The time interval in between denoise runs (in seconds)</span></p><p><strong>LogInfo</strong><br/><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Output logging info</span></p><p><strong>Min Samples</strong><br/><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">The minimum number of average samples per bucket before the interactive denoiser runs for the first time.  Changing this preference requires the render to be restarted for this option to be respected</span><br/><br/><br/></p><p /><div class=\"embeddedObject conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"8e51d9c0-51b2-4ddb-8b74-749411be9713\" data-macro-id=\"82dd2c89-69d5-4cd9-accf-43c4b65d3a3a\" data-macro-name=\"multimedia\">\n    <video src=\"/wiki/download/attachments/546179198/KatanaDenoiser.mp4\" height=\"540\" width=\"960\" autoplay=\"\" controls=\"\">\n        Your browser does not support the HTML5 video element\n</video>\n\n</div>"
